    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1796310/extras/2ada9a0b3d821afdf009e8b8f60dc39e.poster.avif?t=1729922557\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1796310/extras/2ada9a0b3d821afdf009e8b8f60dc39e.webm?t=1729922557\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1796310/extras/2ada9a0b3d821afdf009e8b8f60dc39e.mp4?t=1729922557\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Pamali: The Vengeful Mother</strong> 是 Storytale 的 <strong>Pamali: Indonesian Folklore Horror</strong> 系列中的一款新的民间传说。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一款 1-4 人在线合作生存恐怖游戏。利用每个角色的独特优势，与队友一起制定战略，竭尽全力拯救失踪的孩子，逃离被遗弃的孤儿院。带上您的朋友一起来吧！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >民间传说</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2022 年，印度尼西亚中爪哇的某座山上。你和你的三个儿时玩伴在太阳落山后冒险闯入一所废弃的孤儿院。传闻这座废弃的孤儿院是 “Wewe Gombel ”的巢穴，“Wewe Gombel ”是一个以绑架儿童闻名的精灵。你找到了进入建筑的方法，但突然间，所有的门都被封死了。你的冒险变成了噩梦般的现实。  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >你准备好了吗？</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>单人或最多 4 名玩家一起玩</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1796310/extras/ecdb932116d5e25993d6d98f6d76fa10.poster.avif?t=1729922557\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1796310/extras/ecdb932116d5e25993d6d98f6d76fa10.webm?t=1729922557\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1796310/extras/ecdb932116d5e25993d6d98f6d76fa10.mp4?t=1729922557\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong> </strong>不要害怕！最多可与 4 名玩家联手，体验真正令人不寒而栗的游戏。俗话说，人多力量大，有朋友在身边，等待着你的恐怖将更容易承受。不过别担心，如果你喜欢独自冒险，我们也会支持你，尽管这并不是在公园里散步。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>选择你的幸存者</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1796310/extras/f7460f1ed7346745f014af5ed5e0a728.poster.avif?t=1729922557\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1796310/extras/f7460f1ed7346745f014af5ed5e0a728.webm?t=1729922557\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1796310/extras/f7460f1ed7346745f014af5ed5e0a728.mp4?t=1729922557\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong></strong>从 4 个独特的角色中选择，每个角色都有自己独特的优势。无论你是能看到灵魂的人，还是力量强大的人，是灵活敏捷的短跑选手，还是精通技术的天才，你的选择都很重要。你们的不同优势相互补充，共同为生存铺平道路。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>身临其境的游戏体验</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1796310/extras/17b1954f89a1c7ebb8e0ecded4b03e3c.poster.avif?t=1729922557\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1796310/extras/17b1954f89a1c7ebb8e0ecded4b03e3c.webm?t=1729922557\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong></strong>您所做的、所看到的或所说的将是决定您将经历的体验的关键因素。利用你的独特优势来防御、分散敌人的注意力或削弱敌人的力量，拯救失踪的孩子，并最终逃出生天！你将遇到的恐怖事件几乎都是有意为之，都是基于你自己的行为。谨慎行动，明智思考。<strong> </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><strong>发现多重结局</strong></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1796310/extras/64c2cb4a77a6d513c82a3a26978d8602.poster.avif?t=1729922557\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1796310/extras/64c2cb4a77a6d513c82a3a26978d8602.webm?t=1729922557\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1796310/extras/64c2cb4a77a6d513c82a3a26978d8602.mp4?t=1729922557\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><strong></strong></strong>如果是你，你会怎么做？在玩游戏的过程中，你会发现自己每次都会遇到许多不同的情况。您在游戏中做出的决定将引导您走向不同的路线和结局。<strong> </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><strong>文化之旅</strong></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1796310/extras/c2097df64028dc1baa9219e17924da5f.poster.avif?t=1729922557\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1796310/extras/c2097df64028dc1baa9219e17924da5f.webm?t=1729922557\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1796310/extras/c2097df64028dc1baa9219e17924da5f.mp4?t=1729922557\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> </strong>游戏中的幽灵、场景、事件和传说都取材于真实的印尼文化。你将了解到所有塑造恐怖故事本身的怪异文化。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >准备好与朋友或独自面对恐惧吧。选择你的角色，做出决定，揭开潜伏在黑暗中的谜团。恐怖在等待着您......</h2>",
